{"tid":1957101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衛生部長：利物浦對馬德里如期作賽是錯誤","createTime":"2020-04-03T15:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T06:03:32.000Z","uid":62257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52e1671363487b2ec893c6044098b6e97898cc79","tid":1957101,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=29045094306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D29045094306&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQymyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=ea5f633f\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=29045094306</a><br />\n【Now Sports】利物浦公共衛生部長承認，在新型冠狀病毒爆發下，利物浦早前與馬德里體育會的歐聯比賽繼續進行是一大錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦公共衛生部長馬菲艾斯頓（Matthew Ashton）指出，現時利物浦市的新型冠狀病毒病例的上升，有可能是受到利物浦與馬德里體育會的歐聯比賽影響。於3月20日前，利物浦只得14宗確診個案，兩星期內卻增加至309宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n艾斯頓說：「這不是一個正確的决定，人們不會故意作出錯誤的决定，也許當時政府並沒理解這種情況的嚴重性，不過我們永遠不會知道，馬德里體育會的比賽，可能是影響利物浦集會之一。」<br />\n<br />\n該場比賽有近5.4萬名球迷入場，不排除有球迷在這比賽中染病：「這絕對是一個被列入學習和未來調查的名單，這樣大家就可以學習，而不會犯類似的錯誤。」<br />\n<br />\n紅軍於2月中作客負馬德里體育會0:1，到上月中主場90分鐘贏回1:0，及至加時負2:3，兩回合總計負2:4無緣入8強。"},{"pid":"19fd4d67875fbfc36f501bac5ccdfd620406370b","tid":1957101,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef94e68b1290bc077c6a019daa2dccf7da351f7d","tid":1957101,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef7b10aff5e7e93def91d80bb4506c00fc6d519d","tid":1957101,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef94e68b1290bc077c6a019daa2dccf7da351f7d","tid":1957101,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T01:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b42a337d10dffb4c8920923d271d43d7c15ff79","tid":1957101,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T01:55:51.000Z","msg":"唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bafe0c2f90419757c8f4d672f16a394c146457","tid":1957101,"uid":288478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"又柒一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}